Text: thx for the add, hope they don't ruin it in the movie adaptation

While I appreciate that someone took the time to copy all the pages from the book, i have to say, that if you're a bootlegger take some fucking pride in your work.

These pages are warped and cut terribly, as well as dated by when he scanned them. They're all out of order and therefore nearly impossible to read. The first few pages are fine, but then after that, it's totally fucked.
